casebody.data:
Wednesday, October 30, 1991

MERIT DOCKET

91-1624. State, ex rel. Martinelli, v. Wilkinson.

In Procedendo. On answer of respondent. Answer treated as motion to dismiss. Motion to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Wright and Resnick, JJ., concur. Douglas and H. Brown, JJ., would also deny the motions for default judgment and summary judgment.
